                  <li>Wed 12/10/25</li>
              </ul>

              <h3>
                  <a href="https://www.pca.org/news/bylaw-revisions" target="_blank">
                      In accordance with the National Bylaws, the Executive Council has proposed amendments to the PCA Bylaws. 
                  </a>
              </h3>
              <p>The proposed revisions with the rationale are now available for membership review, question, and comment on pca.org. The review period per the Bylaws will be open through January 27, 2026. </p>
