        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-xs-12 col-sm-4 blog-post">
          <div class="blog_inner">
            <div class="blog-img"> 
              <h6><a href="https://pca.org/tag/TechTacticsLive"> <span class="entry-date bold pca-clubblau">#TECHTACTICSLIVE</span></a></h6> 
            			<a href="https://pca.org/news/protect-your-investment-navigating-diminished-value-claims-tech-tactics-live">
            		<img src="https://mediaassets.pca.org/pages/pca/images/content/leadttl-diminished-value-2.jpg" alt="Porsche Club of America - Protect Your Investment: Navigating Diminished Value Claims with Super Car Claims | Tech Tactics Live" style="max-width:406px; max-height:236px; height:auto; border:1px solid #999;"> </a> 
            </div>
            <!--blog-img-->
            <div class="blog-info" style="padding-top:7px;">
              <ul class="post-meta">
                <li>Tue 03/24/26</li>
                <li style="float:right;">by <a href="https://pca.org/author/PCA-YouTube">PCA YouTube</a> </li>
              </ul>
              <h3> 
              			<a href="https://pca.org/news/protect-your-investment-navigating-diminished-value-claims-tech-tactics-live">
              		Protect Your Investment: Navigating Diminished Value Claims with Super Car Claims | Tech Tactics Live</a></h3>
              <p>Steven Calamusa, PCA member and Super Car Claims founder, will be on Tech Tactics Live Wednesday, March 25, at 8 PM ET to answer all your questions about diminished value claims. This will be a popular episode since it covers not only Porsches but any of your cars that qualify. You’ll hear about real life examples of what happens when things to wrong and how to be reimbursed to the fullest.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!--blog_inner--> 
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-xs-12 col-sm-4 blog-post">
          <div class="blog_inner">
            <div class="blog-img"> 
              <h6><a href="https://pca.org/tag/MartFresh"> <span class="entry-date bold pca-clubblau">#MARTFRESH</span></a></h6> 
            			<a href="https://pca.org/news/1977-porsche-924-1999-boxster-2001-911-carrera-cabriolet-or-2018-panamera-turbo-sport-turismo-mart-fresh">
