              		1977 Porsche 924, 1999 Boxster, 2001 911 Carrera Cabriolet, or 2018 Panamera Turbo Sport Turismo? | Mart Fresh</a></h3>
              <p>Mart Fresh is a bi-weekly column in which we pick what we think are the "freshest" Porsches currently available, and then attempt to explain our reasoning. Up this week are a 1977 924, 1999 Boxster, 2001 911 Carrera Cabriolet, and 2018 Panamera Turbo Sport Turismo?</p>
